{"tid":843962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國中央電視台　要求 英國保守黨 道歉 及 保障 言論自由","createTime":"2018-10-01T13:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T15:33:25.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dbdef744a00359793ccbf3a56ffc55523f0b3a22","tid":843962,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:44:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chinaplus.cri.cn/news/china/9/20181001/190886.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinaplus.cri.cn%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F9%2F20181001%2F190886.html&d=bhgyCO6mn7isTI%2FN8FzTojA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=57ad32bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinaplus.cri.cn/news/china/9/20181001/190886.html</a><br />\n<br />\nCCTV demands apology from UK Conservative Party<br />\n<br />\nChina Plus Published: 2018-10-01 18:17:16<br />\n<br />\nChina Central Television has lodged an official protest to UK authorities over the treatment of a Chinese journalist in Birmingham, Britain.<br />\n<br />\nDuring its annual session on Sunday, the Human Rights Commission of the UK Conservative Party held a sideline meeting on Hong Kong, inviting so-called Hong Kong independence activists that had organized the Occupy Central movement in the territory.<br />\n<br />\nCCTV journalist based in the UK, Kong Linlin, expressed her views when raising questions, becoming obstructed and even physically harrassed.<br />\n<br />\nA spokesperson of CCTV is calling it unacceptable that the legal rights of a Chinese journalist were violated in the UK, which CCTV notes often flaunts freedom of speech.<br />\n<br />\nCCTV says it strongly protests the incident, and is demanding an official apology from the event's organizer.<br />\n<br />\nIt's also calling on U.K. police to safeguard the legitimate rights of the Chinese journalist.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/10/cctv-uk3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fcctv-uk3%2F&d=bhgyCO6mn7isTI%2FN8FzTojA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2af5dec4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/10/cctv-uk3/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CCTV-UK-3-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FCCTV-UK-3-2.jpg&h=84d4f956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國中央電視台話英國保守黨人權委員會昨日舉行香港座談會，請佔中港獨派人士出席，中央電視台駐英記者孔琳琳，表達觀點，受到阻撓甚至身體騷擾，中央電視台強烈抗議，要求該活動組織者道歉，並且呼籲英國警方維護中國記者的合法權利。實情係：昨日的香港座談會主題係香港自治自由受中國蠶食，英國身為中英聯合聲明簽約國，有責任維護一國兩制。出席的香港政治人物包括羅冠聰、李柱銘、戴耀廷，皆聲稱不支持港獨或非港獨。會議尾聲，據Hong Kong Watch 影片顯示，一名CCTV女記者尖叫辱罵人權委員會副主席羅傑斯Benedict Rogers欲分裂中國，在場義工勸其離去，中國女記者暴粗，鬧英國假民主，而且毆打在場香港義工Enoch Liu，後警方來到將中國女記者帶走。"},{"pid":"d63fd31af1b350f2be733664c89f7796a7e77192","tid":843962,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20181001134501im_/http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CCTV-UK-3-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20181001134501im_%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FCCTV-UK-3-2.jpg&h=ccf057da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"393b65cef84708024eaab6c1661e0a9d2e9bc632","tid":843962,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"隻生番無投訴錯喎:<br />\n假民主<br />\n言論自由<br />\n呢啲係香港大問題呀"},{"pid":"7af821bde3c59e66dbe1c4981fa6c05a13f0bd7f","tid":843962,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/215053_8b24464415c1a67ca3b936a49853f273.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F215053_8b24464415c1a67ca3b936a49853f273.png&h=1a276e9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f496c8ebf4c16477a535eb28dd78008bf45b594","tid":